  <title translate="true">BorderColor Property</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">BorderColor property</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">BorderColor Property</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Specifies the color of the border of a control. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Inline heading"><text styleclass="Inline heading" translate="true">Syntax</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">Control.BorderColor = nColor</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Inline heading"><text styleclass="Inline heading" translate="true">Parameters</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Parameter"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">nColor</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Explanation"><text styleclass="Explanation" translate="true">Specifies the border color value.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Inline heading"><text styleclass="Inline heading" translate="true">Remarks</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Applies to: </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Signature_Control" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Signature</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">&#32;</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">BorderColor only applies to a Signature control when the BorderStyle property is 1 - FixedSingle.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Inline heading"><text styleclass="Inline heading" translate="true">See also</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="BorderStyle_property" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">BorderStyle property</link></para>
  </body>
</topic>
